OL,5, Kyle Newton was hoping for a break in  
OL,6, the resort of Sanya on Hainan island - 
OL,7, known as "China's Hawaii" - after      
OL,8, enduring a harsh two-month Covid       
OL,9, lockdown in Shanghai.                  
OL,11,FHis Hainan trip was due to last less   
OL,12,Fthan a week and was the teacher's first
OL,13,Fholiday in China since arriving just as
OL,14,Fthe pandemic broke out. The island lies
OL,15,Fin the South China Sea just off China's
OL,16,Fsouthern coast.                        
OL,18,FBut on Saturday, after 263 positive    
OL,19,Fcases were confirmed in Sanya,         
OL,20,Fauthorities cancelled all flights and  
OL,21,Ftrains out of the city.                
